---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle="404 Not Found">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-slate-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 md:py-16">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-800/90 to-slate-800/95 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-xl border border-slate-700/50 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-sm relative overflow-hidden text-center">
        <!-- Background tech pattern -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-tech-grid bg-tech-grid opacity-5 pointer-events-none"></div>
        
        <!-- Content wrapper with z-index -->
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <!-- 404 Icon -->
          <div class="mb-8">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500/20 to-orange-500/20 rounded-full border border-red-400/30 mb-6">
              <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-2.5L13.732 4c-.77-.833-1.732-.833-2.5 0L4.314 16.5c-.77.833.192 2.5 1.732 2.5z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Error Code -->
          <h1 class="text-8xl md:text-9xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-red-400 via-orange-400 to-red-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4 leading-none">
            404
          </h1>
          
          <!-- Error Title -->
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            ページが見つかりませんでした
          </h2>
          
          <!-- Error Description -->
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            お探しのページは移動、削除、または一時的に利用できない状態です。<br/>
            URLをご確認いただくか、下記のボタンからトップページにお戻りください。
          </p>
          
          <!-- Action Buttons -->
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center mb-8">
            <a 
              href="/" 
              class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-blue-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:from-cyan-600 hover:to-blue-700 hover:shadow-xl transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300"
            >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"/>
              </svg>
              トップページへ戻る
            </a>
            
            <a 
              href="/search" 
              class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 font-semibold rounded-lg border border-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-600 hover:text-white hover:border-slate-500 transition-all duration-300"
            >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/>
              </svg>
              記事を検索
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Additional Help -->
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">
            <p>それでも問題が解決しない場合は、<a href="/contact" class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 underline transition-colors">お問い合わせページ</a>からご連絡ください。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout> 